graph TB
    Comerciante["👤 <b>Comerciante (Carlos)</b>"]
    Ops["🛠️ <b>Operador (Ops)</b>"]

    subgraph Sistema["🏦 Sistema CashFlow"]
        IdentityAPI["🔐 <b>Identity API</b><br/>[ASP.NET Core 10]<br/><i>Auth: login, refresh,<br/>logout. Emite JWT.<br/>(ADR-027)</i>"]

        TransactionsAPI["📦 <b>Transactions API</b><br/>[ASP.NET Core 10]<br/><i>Write side — registra<br/>débitos e créditos.<br/>Publica eventos via Outbox.<br/>Valida JWT.</i>"]

        BalanceAPI["📊 <b>Balance API</b><br/>[ASP.NET Core 10]<br/><i>Read side puro — expõe<br/>GET /balance. Sem broker,<br/>sem migrations.</i>"]

        BalanceWorker["⚙️ <b>Balance Worker</b><br/>[.NET Worker Service]<br/><i>Consumer + ConsolidationService.<br/>Dono das migrations do<br/>schema balance. (ADR-026)</i>"]

        AdminAPI["🚨 <b>Admin API</b><br/>[ASP.NET Core 10]<br/><i>Ops da DLQ: count<br/>+ redeliver. Sem Postgres.<br/>(ADR-028)</i>"]

        RabbitMQ["📮 <b>RabbitMQ</b><br/>[Broker AMQP + plugin<br/>delayed-message-exchange]<br/><i>TransactionRegistered<br/>+ DLQ visível</i>"]

        DBIdentity["🗄️ <b>Postgres — schema 'identity'</b><br/>[PostgreSQL 16]<br/><i>app_users + refresh_tokens.<br/>user: app_identity<br/>(GRANT restrito)</i>"]

        DBTransactions["🗄️ <b>Postgres — schema 'transactions'</b><br/>[PostgreSQL 16]<br/><i>transactions + outbox_events.<br/>user: app_transactions<br/>(GRANT restrito)</i>"]

        DBBalance["🗄️ <b>Postgres — schema 'balance'</b><br/>[PostgreSQL 16]<br/><i>daily_balance + processed_events.<br/>user: app_balance<br/>(GRANT restrito)</i>"]
    end

    Comerciante -->|"POST /api/v1/auth/login<br/>POST /api/v1/auth/refresh<br/>POST /api/v1/auth/logout<br/>(HTTPS/JSON)"| IdentityAPI
    Comerciante -->|"POST /api/v1/transactions<br/>Bearer JWT<br/>(HTTPS/JSON)"| TransactionsAPI
    Comerciante -->|"GET /api/v1/balance/{date}<br/>Bearer JWT<br/>(HTTPS/JSON)"| BalanceAPI
    Ops -->|"GET /api/v1/admin/errors/count<br/>POST /api/v1/admin/errors/redeliver<br/>Bearer JWT (ADR-028 → RequireAdmin)"| AdminAPI

    IdentityAPI -->|"SELECT/INSERT/UPDATE<br/>app_users, refresh_tokens<br/>(Dapper UoW)"| DBIdentity
    TransactionsAPI -->|"INSERT transaction + outbox<br/>(Dapper UoW atômica)"| DBTransactions
    TransactionsAPI -.->|"OutboxDispatcher<br/>publica TransactionRegistered<br/>(AMQP)"| RabbitMQ

    RabbitMQ -->|"Consume TransactionRegistered<br/>(AMQP, at-least-once,<br/>SAC + PrefetchCount=1)"| BalanceWorker
    BalanceWorker -->|"UPSERT daily_balance<br/>+ INSERT processed_events<br/>(Dapper, transação atômica)"| DBBalance
    BalanceWorker -.->|"DLQ: balance.transaction-registered_error<br/>(após esgotar retries)"| RabbitMQ

    BalanceAPI -->|"SELECT daily_balance<br/>(read-only)"| DBBalance
    AdminAPI -->|"BasicGet + BasicPublish<br/>(RabbitMQ.Client direto)"| RabbitMQ

